{"tid":1115620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Uber上市】Uber掛牌前夕 再獲三日企支持 共投資78億港元","createTime":"2019-04-19T10:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T10:37:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80177de0a9bb17b2e0178406f054ae7d60ea967c","tid":1115620,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190419/s00010/034d0df9e3cf536dc816e8bc01ea0d46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190419%2Fs00010%2F034d0df9e3cf536dc816e8bc01ea0d46.jpg&h=87f35c19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCall車App Uber在美國即將上市前夕，再次獲得投資者支持。據彭博報道，Uber Technologies Inc.獲得三家日本公司共計10億美元(約78億港元)的投資。<br />\n<br />\n據報道引述Uber的聲明稱，日本電裝、豐田汽車和軟銀集團旗下的願景基金入股Uber自動駕駛業務，該業務的估值約為72.5億美元。<br />\n<br />\nUber表示，豐田和電裝一起投資6.67億美元；而願景基金則投資3.33億美元。截至目前為止，軟銀已是Uber最大股東，持股比例為16%。"},{"pid":"3803588eda8f01677f3e661d2de9b908e7848624","tid":1115620,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"All in美股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b05cdb44cfb43aeda1f10ed349ba2b7ced5241f","tid":1115620,"uid":159308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3803588eda8f01677f3e661d2de9b908e7848624","tid":1115620,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"All in美股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"幾時上？"},{"pid":"eaabcb6c2cd2d6c8f03ccc0a6bc07462dae576e1","tid":1115620,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:21:35.000Z","msg":"呢兩日搭咗三程，成$400，爽！"},{"pid":"5e6536ac5f3c3270aa6f8b7f6b5e67164155774b","tid":1115620,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"a9dd5ae8dc8ff51d2124e177fb8deb0a2c40eb4e","tid":1115620,"uid":